1
00:00:00,970 --> 00:00:03,780
Hey, all you viewers out there!

2
00:00:03,780 --> 00:00:07,180
When you're watchin' Fairy Tail, make 
sure to keep the room nice and bright,

3
00:00:07,180 --> 00:00:09,240
and sit back from the screen, 'kay?

4
00:00:10,590 --> 00:00:13,000
Previously on Fairy Tail!

5
00:00:13,540 --> 00:00:18,370
Amazingly, it turns out Lucy is the daughter of the Heartfilia Konzern!

6
00:00:18,510 --> 00:00:20,310
How surprising...

7
00:00:20,310 --> 00:00:27,840
Phantom Lord was after her, but thanks to the master invoking Fairy Law, our battle with them is finally over.

8
00:00:27,840 --> 00:00:29,140
However...

9
00:00:49,220 --> 00:00:53,630
It'll be all right! I'll yell it out countless times.

10
00:00:53,630 --> 00:00:58,700
I believe your every tomorrow will be shining.

11
00:00:58,700 --> 00:01:01,050
The intersection of all people

12
00:01:01,050 --> 00:01:03,660
whose dreams have come true is one point:

13
00:01:03,660 --> 00:01:08,290
Never giving up.  And that's why we're not gonna lose!

14
00:01:08,290 --> 00:01:13,470
When it seems like you'll be blown away by the headwinds,

15
00:01:13,470 --> 00:01:15,620
grasp this hand, try to take a chance.

16
00:01:15,620 --> 00:01:18,890
Because you're not alone anymore, got it?

17
00:01:22,010 --> 00:01:24,000
Go forward, more and more!

18
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:26,520
Don't give up on your awesome dream!

19
00:01:26,520 --> 00:01:27,780
That's right, don't cry!

20
00:01:27,780 --> 00:01:29,250
Move on, my way!

21
00:01:29,250 --> 00:01:31,630
Now, with the light shining down upon you.

22
00:01:31,630 --> 00:01:33,710
Don't even think about something like giving up!

23
00:01:33,710 --> 00:01:36,140
Even if you trade being hurt again for strength.

24
00:01:36,140 --> 00:01:41,630
Your eyes, always looking straight ahead,

25
00:01:41,630 --> 00:01:45,910
can surely see the light!

26
00:02:05,030 --> 00:02:08,510
Everyone seems really happy, Lucy.

27
00:02:08,510 --> 00:02:09,410
Yeah...

28
00:02:12,040 --> 00:02:13,740
Lucy?

29
00:02:17,250 --> 00:02:18,950
My Resolve.

30
00:02:21,790 --> 00:02:24,970
Hey, can you hear me, Gajeel?

31
00:02:24,970 --> 00:02:27,130
I can't hear nothin'.

32
00:02:27,440 --> 00:02:31,580
So hey, where'd you learn Dragon Slayer magic?

33
00:02:31,580 --> 00:02:34,550
I said I couldn't hear you!

34
00:02:34,550 --> 00:02:38,690
I've never met anyone who used the same magic as me.

35
00:02:38,690 --> 00:02:40,800
You could at least tell me that much!

36
00:02:40,800 --> 00:02:42,410
Oh, shut it.

37
00:02:43,600 --> 00:02:45,340
Metalicana.

38
00:02:45,970 --> 00:02:48,820
The Iron Dragon, Metalicana.

39
00:02:48,820 --> 00:02:50,080
What?

40
00:02:51,820 --> 00:02:54,540
I knew it! You were taught by a dragon?

41
00:02:54,540 --> 00:02:55,950
You too?

42
00:02:55,950 --> 00:02:57,670
So where is it now?

43
00:02:57,670 --> 00:02:58,900
Who knows?

44
00:03:00,290 --> 00:03:02,340
Where is it now?!

45
00:03:02,340 --> 00:03:04,210
I said I didn't know!

46
00:03:08,540 --> 00:03:10,450
Man...

47
00:03:10,450 --> 00:03:14,850
Just talkin' to you makes my brains turn to mush.

48
00:03:14,850 --> 00:03:16,490
Say that again!

49
00:03:18,060 --> 00:03:19,910
It disappeared.

50
00:03:20,710 --> 00:03:25,390
One day, Metalicana suddenly vanished.

51
00:03:25,390 --> 00:03:28,230
Without saying a thing.

52
00:03:28,230 --> 00:03:31,780
Man... What a selfish jerk.

53
00:03:33,710 --> 00:03:38,040
Wait, that wasn't 7 years ago on July 7th, was it?

54
00:03:38,040 --> 00:03:42,050
Wait... Do you know where Metalicana is?

55
00:03:42,050 --> 00:03:47,800
Not a chance. I'm looking for Igneel, a fire dragon.

56
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:51,160
He also disappeared 7 years ago on July 7th.

57
00:03:51,760 --> 00:03:53,360
7 years ago...

58
00:03:53,360 --> 00:03:57,330
Year 777, Month 7, Day 7...

59
00:03:57,330 --> 00:03:59,800
On that day two dragons disappeared...

60
00:03:59,800 --> 00:04:01,800
Why is it a bunch of sevens lined up?!

61
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:03,390
How the hell should I know?

62
00:04:05,550 --> 00:04:08,160
Not like I care anyway.

63
00:04:10,030 --> 00:04:11,800
If you're leavin', then scat already.

64
00:04:11,800 --> 00:04:14,100
This is <i>our</i> guild!

65
00:04:14,100 --> 00:04:16,560
You're the one that should get out!

66
00:04:17,050 --> 00:04:18,960
Man, why so picky?

67
00:04:18,960 --> 00:04:20,460
Get out now!

68
00:04:20,780 --> 00:04:23,660
Give me a call if you find anything about Igneel, 'kay?

69
00:04:23,660 --> 00:04:27,410
Why the hell should I be nice to you, huh?

70
00:04:27,970 --> 00:04:30,240
Because we're both Dragon Slayers!

71
00:04:30,240 --> 00:04:33,870
Don't give me that crap! Next time we meet, I'll kick your ass!

72
00:04:33,870 --> 00:04:35,500
I guarantee it!

73
00:04:35,500 --> 00:04:37,370
Make sure you've said your prayers.

74
00:04:37,370 --> 00:04:39,430
You're dangerous, you know that?

75
00:04:39,430 --> 00:04:42,700
I thought we could call it even now and make up...

76
00:04:42,700 --> 00:04:44,530
You're the one that's dangerous!

77
00:04:44,530 --> 00:04:47,170
Just look at what you did to our guild!

78
00:04:47,170 --> 00:04:50,670
Well, you busted up our guild first!

79
00:04:51,080 --> 00:04:53,770
I knew it! I give up makin' nice with you!

80
00:04:59,700 --> 00:05:04,040
They've really made a big mess now...

81
00:05:05,470 --> 00:05:08,570
U-Um... Master...

82
00:05:11,300 --> 00:05:15,380
You've really had a tough time, I know.

83
00:05:15,380 --> 00:05:17,880
Don't give us that face, Lu-chan!

84
00:05:18,490 --> 00:05:19,800
We're back!

85
00:05:20,510 --> 00:05:22,180
Levy-chan!

86
00:05:22,180 --> 00:05:25,200
Everyone worked together to beat them.

87
00:05:25,200 --> 00:05:27,220
Although the guild was destroyed.

88
00:05:27,220 --> 00:05:30,020
We all just need to rebuild it.

89
00:05:30,020 --> 00:05:31,060
Oui.

90
00:05:31,060 --> 00:05:32,490
You guys...

91
00:05:32,490 --> 00:05:35,250
Sorry for making you worry, Lu-chan.

92
00:05:36,130 --> 00:05:38,810
No! This is all my...

93
00:05:38,810 --> 00:05:40,700
I heard.

94
00:05:40,700 --> 00:05:44,660
But nobody thinks this is your fault, Lu-chan.

95
00:05:44,660 --> 00:05:48,950
On the other hand... I'm sorry I couldn't be more help.

96
00:05:48,950 --> 00:05:50,620
Lucy.

97
00:05:51,990 --> 00:05:56,670
Fun things, sad things... We can't share everything,

98
00:05:56,670 --> 00:05:58,800
but what we can, we should share...

99
00:05:58,800 --> 00:06:01,010
That's what it means to be a guild.

100
00:06:01,010 --> 00:06:03,850
A single person's happiness is everyone's happiness.

101
00:06:03,850 --> 00:06:06,380
A single person's anger is everyone's anger.

102
00:06:06,380 --> 00:06:10,980
And a single person's tears are everyone's tears.

103
00:06:10,980 --> 00:06:14,380
You have no reason to feel guilty.

104
00:06:14,770 --> 00:06:20,190
Lucy... You should be able to tell how everyone feels...

105
00:06:26,050 --> 00:06:28,680
Raise your head!

106
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:33,210
You're part of the Fairy Tail family.

107
00:06:52,670 --> 00:06:55,030
Although...

108
00:06:55,030 --> 00:06:57,400
We went a bit overboard...

109
00:06:57,400 --> 00:07:00,080
This is going to seriously anger the Council...

110
00:07:00,080 --> 00:07:04,610
Or wait, if it goes poorly, maybe even imprisonment...

111
00:07:06,110 --> 00:07:07,890
Master!

112
00:07:07,890 --> 00:07:10,770
And so...

113
00:07:11,310 --> 00:07:14,380
It's been one week since our battle with Phantom ended.

114
00:07:15,230 --> 00:07:19,040
We've finally gotten back our peaceful days...

115
00:07:19,040 --> 00:07:21,960
Everyone, let's take a break!

116
00:07:23,070 --> 00:07:27,130
Although after it happened, it's been super tough.

117
00:07:27,130 --> 00:07:31,470
We were rounded up by the Council's army, the Rune Knights.

118
00:07:31,470 --> 00:07:32,740
This ain't good...

119
00:07:32,740 --> 00:07:33,970
They've already caught wind?

120
00:07:33,970 --> 00:07:34,980
Run for it!

121
00:07:34,980 --> 00:07:36,850
Aye, sir!

122
00:07:36,850 --> 00:07:40,990
That's not going to work Natsu. You can't get away from the Rune Knights.

123
00:07:41,820 --> 00:07:43,550
Master, hang in there!

124
00:07:45,080 --> 00:07:50,740
We were dragged to the army post to be interviewed about what had happened.

125
00:07:50,740 --> 00:07:56,540
Every day they'd question us, but finally after a week, it calmed down.

126
00:07:57,330 --> 00:08:03,760
It seems like Fairy Tail's punishment will be handed down from the Council at a later date.

127
00:08:06,130 --> 00:08:08,940
But, don't worry Mom.

128
00:08:08,940 --> 00:08:12,090
I don't think it'll be that bad of a punishment.

129
00:08:12,090 --> 00:08:17,540
Since the circumstantial evidence and witness reports all point to an attack from Phantom.

130
00:08:20,810 --> 00:08:23,940
I hope these bruises goes away...

131
00:08:30,270 --> 00:08:36,580
So, Mom... Do you think <i>he</i> was behind the whole thing, pulling the strings?

132
00:08:37,350 --> 00:08:39,810
I know what he's like, but to go this far...

133
00:08:43,160 --> 00:08:47,970
No, he'd do it. He wouldn't have any problem with this.

134
00:08:48,820 --> 00:08:53,560
But why would he suddenly try and take me back?

135
00:08:54,020 --> 00:08:56,460
It's not like he cares about me personally.

136
00:08:58,870 --> 00:09:00,020
Mom...

137
00:09:00,910 --> 00:09:06,380
He'll do it again, won't he? Using the power of his money...

138
00:09:07,390 --> 00:09:08,780
That...

139
00:09:10,060 --> 00:09:11,280
...I couldn't...

140
00:09:16,650 --> 00:09:17,880
Oh, my...

141
00:09:17,880 --> 00:09:20,360
That's 'cause you tried to carry so many at once, idiot.

142
00:09:20,360 --> 00:09:21,910
What'd you call me?

143
00:09:21,910 --> 00:09:23,330
You wanna go?

144
00:09:23,330 --> 00:09:25,630
You're carrying them so daintily!

145
00:09:25,630 --> 00:09:28,250
Gray-sama, carry me too!

146
00:09:28,250 --> 00:09:29,490
You, over there!

147
00:09:30,330 --> 00:09:32,560
Less talking, more working!

148
00:09:32,560 --> 00:09:35,490
We're going to rebuild Fairy Tail ASAP!

149
00:09:35,490 --> 00:09:36,160
'Kay...

150
00:09:36,160 --> 00:09:37,980
Erza's really into it...

151
00:09:37,980 --> 00:09:40,140
She can requip to an outfit like that?

152
00:09:41,140 --> 00:09:43,610
Master's also really getting into it!

153
00:09:43,610 --> 00:09:45,470
He sure is!

154
00:09:45,470 --> 00:09:48,010
Foreman, where do you need this timber?

155
00:09:48,010 --> 00:09:49,810
Oh, over there!

156
00:09:49,810 --> 00:09:51,840
Who is she calling foreman?

157
00:09:51,840 --> 00:09:54,130
Damn it! I hate losing!

158
00:09:54,130 --> 00:09:55,990
Ooh, it's whack-a-mole!

159
00:09:55,990 --> 00:09:56,920
Wait...

160
00:09:56,920 --> 00:09:58,940
Isn't it kind of big?

161
00:09:58,940 --> 00:10:01,220
While we're at it, we're expanding.

162
00:10:01,220 --> 00:10:03,520
See? Here's what it'll look like when it's finished.

163
00:10:03,520 --> 00:10:04,090
Seriously?

164
00:10:04,090 --> 00:10:05,300
Let's have a look.

165
00:10:05,300 --> 00:10:07,160
It would be fine without changing it.

166
00:10:07,160 --> 00:10:08,960
What kind of guild is it going to be like?

167
00:10:10,870 --> 00:10:13,050
This is another...

168
00:10:13,390 --> 00:10:14,690
I don't really get it.

169
00:10:14,690 --> 00:10:18,560
But man, this is really crappy. What idiot drew this?

170
00:10:22,260 --> 00:10:23,980
Oh, it was Mira-chan!

171
00:10:23,980 --> 00:10:25,430
You made her cry again.

172
00:10:25,430 --> 00:10:27,340
And such is Gray.

173
00:10:27,340 --> 00:10:31,110
That's right! Gray-sama is only kind to Juvia!

174
00:10:35,310 --> 00:10:36,490
I'm starving!

175
00:10:36,490 --> 00:10:36,970
Aye!

176
00:10:36,970 --> 00:10:38,580
Time to eat?

177
00:10:38,950 --> 00:10:39,990
What's this?

178
00:10:39,990 --> 00:10:41,250
I'm soaked!

179
00:10:41,250 --> 00:10:42,430
It's a lunch box!

180
00:10:42,430 --> 00:10:43,810
A lunch box?

181
00:10:47,460 --> 00:10:48,920
That looks good!

182
00:10:48,920 --> 00:10:52,340
I know! This is called a character lunch!

183
00:10:52,340 --> 00:10:54,520
Can I actually eat something this insane?

184
00:10:54,520 --> 00:10:56,110
It's dripping something...

185
00:10:56,110 --> 00:10:57,740
Then give it to me!

186
00:10:56,700 --> 00:11:01,010
Juvia is heartbroken! She took 3 days and nights straight to make it!

187
00:11:01,010 --> 00:11:03,730
Who said you could eat?

188
00:11:04,140 --> 00:11:06,500
Is that one of those character lunches?

189
00:11:12,240 --> 00:11:14,350
This isn't bad. Give me some more.

190
00:11:14,350 --> 00:11:16,230
Really? I'll eat it too.

191
00:11:16,230 --> 00:11:18,420
Yum! So delicious!

192
00:11:18,420 --> 00:11:19,910
I want to eat it everyday!

193
00:11:19,910 --> 00:11:22,140
Which means... Will you marry me?

194
00:11:22,140 --> 00:11:24,810
Yes! I'll give you 30 babies or more!

195
00:11:24,810 --> 00:11:26,210
Juvia's overwhelmed!

196
00:11:26,210 --> 00:11:28,440
Natsu, Gray, Erza...

197
00:11:29,830 --> 00:11:33,670
Would you give these to Lucy?

198
00:11:33,670 --> 00:11:34,940
They're her keys.

199
00:11:34,940 --> 00:11:35,680
It's you.

200
00:11:35,680 --> 00:11:37,730
I was wondering where you'd gone off to.

201
00:11:37,730 --> 00:11:39,590
You've been searching for these the whole time?

202
00:11:39,590 --> 00:11:42,520
Are you okay? You don't look good at all.

203
00:11:42,520 --> 00:11:45,150
Thanks. I'm fine.

204
00:11:45,150 --> 00:11:48,730
Sheesh... It's hard being a male feminist...

205
00:11:48,730 --> 00:11:53,150
Lucy isn't here. Her injuries hurt so bad she can't move, maybe...

206
00:11:53,150 --> 00:11:54,890
Maybe we should go check on her.

207
00:11:54,890 --> 00:11:55,990
You come too, Loke.

208
00:11:55,990 --> 00:11:57,620
I'll pass.

209
00:11:57,620 --> 00:12:01,240
You know I can't handle Celestial Wizards.

210
00:12:01,240 --> 00:12:02,700
Really?

211
00:12:02,700 --> 00:12:04,630
But Lucy's still Lucy.

212
00:12:04,630 --> 00:12:07,750
Natsu. We all have our weaknesses.

213
00:12:07,750 --> 00:12:09,500
Don't pry.

214
00:12:15,240 --> 00:12:16,780
Karen...

215
00:12:16,780 --> 00:12:21,150
Must you be in such a rush? I...

216
00:12:24,610 --> 00:12:26,120
Lucy!

217
00:12:26,120 --> 00:12:27,610
You feelin' okay?

218
00:12:27,610 --> 00:12:29,650
Don't come in through the window!

219
00:12:29,650 --> 00:12:32,550
Enter through the door, people. The door.

220
00:12:32,550 --> 00:12:34,480
And what the hell are you doing?

221
00:12:34,480 --> 00:12:35,450
Aye.

222
00:12:36,600 --> 00:12:37,970
Huh?

223
00:12:37,970 --> 00:12:39,360
She'd usually be all...

224
00:12:39,360 --> 00:12:41,280
This is my room!

225
00:12:41,280 --> 00:12:43,330
...and stuff.

226
00:12:43,330 --> 00:12:44,520
In the bath?

227
00:12:44,520 --> 00:12:46,540
Gray, you perv!

228
00:12:46,540 --> 00:12:49,590
Something like this was bound to happen eventually...

229
00:12:49,590 --> 00:12:50,870
Pardon the intrusion!

230
00:12:50,870 --> 00:12:51,990
She ain't here.

231
00:12:51,990 --> 00:12:54,860
That's not how it's supposed to go! And get out of there!

232
00:12:54,860 --> 00:12:56,530
Maybe she's out?

233
00:12:56,530 --> 00:12:58,850
Why did you come here, again?

234
00:12:59,410 --> 00:13:01,610
Your straight-man act is lame.

235
00:13:01,610 --> 00:13:03,710
Without Lucy our tempo is all off.

236
00:13:03,710 --> 00:13:07,130
Quit finding fault! And oh, I'm so sorry I suck at comedy.

237
00:13:07,130 --> 00:13:08,290
Lucy!

238
00:13:08,290 --> 00:13:09,450
Hey, you...

239
00:13:09,450 --> 00:13:11,900
What are you people doing?

240
00:13:12,930 --> 00:13:14,640
There's underwear like this?

241
00:13:14,640 --> 00:13:16,850
Underwear? That?

242
00:13:16,850 --> 00:13:20,330
When would you wear such a thing?

243
00:13:20,330 --> 00:13:21,540
When you're eatin'?

244
00:13:21,540 --> 00:13:22,570
No way, no how.

245
00:13:22,570 --> 00:13:23,940
Wait, this is dangerous.

246
00:13:23,940 --> 00:13:25,040
Close the drawer already.

247
00:13:25,040 --> 00:13:27,700
Lucy, come out!

248
00:13:27,700 --> 00:13:29,990
Where have you been searching?

249
00:13:33,180 --> 00:13:34,630
What're these?

250
00:13:34,630 --> 00:13:36,060
Letters?

251
00:13:36,060 --> 00:13:40,480
Mom, I finally joined the guild of my dreams, Fairy Tail...

252
00:13:40,480 --> 00:13:42,970
Hey, don't go reading those!

253
00:13:42,970 --> 00:13:49,150
Today, I met a person named Erza. She's cool and pretty. Then Natsu and Gray...

254
00:13:49,150 --> 00:13:52,000
Are these all letters to her mother?

255
00:13:52,000 --> 00:13:53,310
Looks like it.

256
00:13:53,310 --> 00:13:55,010
I wonder why she didn't send them?

257
00:13:55,010 --> 00:13:56,300
She left a note.

258
00:13:57,220 --> 00:13:59,700
Look, Lucy left a note.

259
00:14:00,250 --> 00:14:01,920
"I will go home."

260
00:14:01,920 --> 00:14:02,950
It seems.

261
00:14:04,180 --> 00:14:06,620
Say what?!

262
00:14:17,220 --> 00:14:20,720
Look! I made your face on a rice ball, Dad!

263
00:14:21,230 --> 00:14:25,810
I made it! Eat up and work hard, 'kay?

264
00:14:26,160 --> 00:14:28,890
I'm working. I'll deal with you later.

265
00:14:28,890 --> 00:14:30,090
Okay...

266
00:14:30,090 --> 00:14:33,200
So I'll leave it right here. Eat it later, 'kay?

267
00:14:33,200 --> 00:14:35,730
And you see, today it's, um...

268
00:14:38,770 --> 00:14:40,620
Did you not hear me?

269
00:14:40,620 --> 00:14:41,890
I'm sorry!

270
00:14:48,960 --> 00:14:49,840
Um...

271
00:14:49,840 --> 00:14:52,260
I said you were bothering me, Lucy!

272
00:14:52,260 --> 00:14:54,750
Our personal chef cooks our food!

273
00:14:54,750 --> 00:15:00,210
If you have time to do that, then you have time to learn something about running an empire!

274
00:15:00,210 --> 00:15:02,420
Understand? Now leave.

275
00:15:03,050 --> 00:15:06,230
Um... Today is...

276
00:15:07,350 --> 00:15:09,650
...my birthday...

277
00:15:15,930 --> 00:15:17,730
Mrs. Spetto!

278
00:15:20,960 --> 00:15:23,820
Madame Lucy!

279
00:15:25,920 --> 00:15:29,470
I'm so glad you're okay, Madame L... Madame L...

280
00:15:29,470 --> 00:15:31,480
I'm sorry for worrying everyone.

281
00:15:31,480 --> 00:15:37,500
M'lady, we have some new reference books from the East...

282
00:15:34,720 --> 00:15:40,940
M'lady, how you've grown... Run off with a lover or two have you?

283
00:15:39,390 --> 00:15:45,350
Have you been keeping up with your magic studies?

284
00:15:41,410 --> 00:15:46,490
I can't believe we get to see you again, M'lady!

285
00:15:47,370 --> 00:15:48,900
There go the waterworks...

286
00:15:48,900 --> 00:15:51,600
You're all the same as ever, I see.

287
00:15:51,600 --> 00:15:56,020
M'lady... M'lord asks you come to the study at the main residence.

288
00:15:58,000 --> 00:16:03,320
He tells his daughter that ran away and came back to report to him?

289
00:16:04,120 --> 00:16:06,410
He hasn't changed either, it seems.

290
00:16:11,150 --> 00:16:13,120
I'd forgotten...

291
00:16:13,780 --> 00:16:18,020
When I lived here, I would wear clothes like this.

292
00:16:18,020 --> 00:16:20,410
Is it too tight?

293
00:16:20,410 --> 00:16:23,320
It's gotten a little small for you, however.

294
00:16:23,320 --> 00:16:24,970
Don't worry.

295
00:16:24,970 --> 00:16:28,280
Oh yeah... I've gotten taller...

296
00:16:30,270 --> 00:16:32,240
Well, I'll be off.

297
00:16:32,240 --> 00:16:33,020
Right!

298
00:16:34,290 --> 00:16:38,730
It's Lucy. I have returned, Father.

299
00:16:38,730 --> 00:16:39,910
Come in.

300
00:16:42,850 --> 00:16:46,950
So you have finally returned, Lucy.

301
00:16:47,720 --> 00:16:49,360
Father...

302
00:16:50,050 --> 00:16:53,490
I apologize for running away from home without saying anything.

303
00:16:53,490 --> 00:16:56,230
I truly regret those actions.

304
00:16:56,230 --> 00:16:59,060
You have made a wise decision.

305
00:16:59,060 --> 00:17:07,550
As long as you are in that guild, I must use my wealth and influence to crush it.

306
00:17:08,790 --> 00:17:12,010
You have finally matured, Lucy.

307
00:17:13,280 --> 00:17:20,730
It seems I've made you realize how much trouble your selfish actions cause for those around you.

308
00:17:22,770 --> 00:17:25,660
You are the daughter of the Heartfilias.

309
00:17:25,660 --> 00:17:27,660
You are not like other people.

310
00:17:27,660 --> 00:17:30,100
You live in different worlds.

311
00:17:30,100 --> 00:17:34,260
It is fortunate that you finally understand this, Lucy.

312
00:17:34,560 --> 00:17:40,120
There is only one reason I've had you returned. A very fortunate event.

313
00:17:40,120 --> 00:17:44,430
A marriage with the son of the Jurener family has been proposed.

314
00:17:44,430 --> 00:17:48,080
Yes... I figured it was something like that.

315
00:17:48,860 --> 00:17:55,540
A marriage with the Jurener family will allow the Heartfilia Railways to make solid strides to the south.

316
00:17:55,540 --> 00:18:00,520
This marriage with ensure our future fortune.

317
00:18:00,520 --> 00:18:02,220
Our fortune?

318
00:18:02,220 --> 00:18:05,230
And you must give birth to a boy.

319
00:18:05,230 --> 00:18:07,480
So he can become heir to the Heartfilia estate.

320
00:18:08,360 --> 00:18:10,230
That is all.

321
00:18:10,230 --> 00:18:11,790
Return to your room.

322
00:18:13,100 --> 00:18:14,760
Father.

323
00:18:14,760 --> 00:18:16,850
You seem to be mistaken.

324
00:18:17,570 --> 00:18:22,330
I have returned in order to show you my resolve.

325
00:18:23,390 --> 00:18:26,880
It's true that I was wrong to leave without saying anything.

326
00:18:27,360 --> 00:18:30,010
It was no different than simply running way.

327
00:18:30,010 --> 00:18:34,970
So this time, I'm going to tell you exactly how I feel before I leave!

328
00:18:36,180 --> 00:18:37,470
Lucy!

329
00:18:37,800 --> 00:18:40,480
There is nothing fortunate about having your fate decided for you!

330
00:18:40,480 --> 00:18:42,980
You must grab your own happiness yourself!

331
00:18:42,980 --> 00:18:44,810
I'm going to walk my own path.

332
00:18:44,810 --> 00:18:47,350
Don't go deciding on who I'll marry.

333
00:18:47,350 --> 00:18:49,190
And...

334
00:18:49,190 --> 00:18:52,200
Do not lay a finger on Fairy Tail again!

335
00:18:58,530 --> 00:19:01,200
The next time you do...

336
00:19:01,200 --> 00:19:06,080
...I, and everyone else in the guild, will consider you the enemy!

337
00:19:08,250 --> 00:19:13,830
If you hadn't done that, maybe we could be a bit more civil.

338
00:19:14,180 --> 00:19:16,800
But it's too late now.

339
00:19:16,800 --> 00:19:19,710
You have hurt my friends far too much.

340
00:19:20,500 --> 00:19:27,190
What I want isn't money, or pretty dresses, or fortune forced upon me...

341
00:19:27,190 --> 00:19:32,140
I'm not Lucky Lucy of the Heartfilias any more...

342
00:19:32,140 --> 00:19:38,210
Fairy Tail is my other family now, and they recognize me just as Lucy!

343
00:19:38,210 --> 00:19:41,380
It's a far more loving family than this!

344
00:19:41,380 --> 00:19:46,900
I only lived here a little while, but leaving the home I lived in with Mother was incredibly difficult.

345
00:19:48,000 --> 00:19:52,420
Mr. Spetto, Old Man Belo, Mr. Ribbon, Mrs. Aed...

346
00:19:52,420 --> 00:19:56,010
It'll be really hard to leave them all...

347
00:19:56,330 --> 00:19:57,410
But...

348
00:19:57,770 --> 00:19:59,580
But, you see...

349
00:20:00,890 --> 00:20:03,820
If Mom was still alive...

350
00:20:03,820 --> 00:20:08,520
I think she'd tell me "You go do what you want to do."

351
00:20:09,180 --> 00:20:10,970
Layla...

352
00:20:12,490 --> 00:20:15,070
Farewell, Dad.

353
00:20:27,480 --> 00:20:28,710
Mom...

354
00:20:37,020 --> 00:20:38,610
Now then...

355
00:20:38,610 --> 00:20:40,490
Lucy!

356
00:20:40,490 --> 00:20:42,510
Lucy!

357
00:20:42,510 --> 00:20:44,060
Why?!

358
00:21:12,560 --> 00:21:15,150
I'm really sorry I worried you all.

359
00:21:15,150 --> 00:21:18,730
Don't worry, it's our fault for jumping to conclusions.

360
00:21:18,730 --> 00:21:20,800
I guess we were worried for nothing.

361
00:21:20,800 --> 00:21:23,090
Happy was crying the whole time.

362
00:21:23,090 --> 00:21:25,770
You were sobbing too, Natsu!

363
00:21:25,770 --> 00:21:27,270
N-No I wasn't!

364
00:21:27,270 --> 00:21:29,390
I'm sorry, really...

365
00:21:29,390 --> 00:21:32,180
But sheesh, what a spacious town.

366
00:21:32,180 --> 00:21:34,330
It's so calm and peaceful.

367
00:21:34,330 --> 00:21:37,850
Oh, this isn't a town. It's our garden.

368
00:21:37,850 --> 00:21:40,640
Our land goes all the way to that mountain over there.

369
00:21:42,470 --> 00:21:43,370
Huh?

370
00:21:43,370 --> 00:21:44,780
What's the matter, everyone?

371
00:21:44,780 --> 00:21:46,000
All Hail, Princess Lucy!

372
00:21:46,000 --> 00:21:47,900
Said it like it's nothin'!

373
00:21:47,900 --> 00:21:50,100
Natsu and Gray have been beaten!

374
00:21:50,100 --> 00:21:52,940
Captain Erza, please, give your orders!

375
00:21:54,310 --> 00:21:56,560
The sky sure is blue...

376
00:21:57,440 --> 00:22:00,400
Captain Erza's malfunctioning!

377
00:22:05,530 --> 00:22:09,600
To Mom up in Heaven, I'm doing well.

378
00:22:10,140 --> 00:22:17,070
You know what Mom? I don't think I can live without my friends.

379
00:22:18,130 --> 00:22:23,380
Since Fairy Tail is already a part of me!

380
00:23:56,490 --> 00:24:01,270
All we've been doing is fighting lately... We'd better do some jobs, or we're in trouble!

381
00:24:01,270 --> 00:24:05,180
I wonder if there's some rough job with a good reward that you can do, Natsu?

382
00:24:05,180 --> 00:24:07,830
I can do delicate work, too!

383
00:24:07,830 --> 00:24:09,110
Not your style.

384
00:24:09,110 --> 00:24:11,740
Alrighty then, let's do it!

385
00:24:11,740 --> 00:24:12,610
It's not your style!

386
00:24:12,610 --> 00:24:14,370
You don't have to repeat it!

387
00:24:14,370 --> 00:24:16,470
Next time: Next Generation!

388
00:24:16,470 --> 00:24:20,220
And wait, do you even know what "delicate" means?

389
00:24:20,220 --> 00:24:21,950
Uh, sure I do.

390
00:24:21,950 --> 00:24:22,950
It's where you don't have to punch things...

391
00:24:22,950 --> 00:24:24,390
Swing and a miss.

392
00:24:24,390 --> 00:24:26,690


